@startuml
!theme plain

title Diagramme de sequence - Prise de rendez-vous

autonumber

actor Patient
boundary Frontend as "Application Angular"
control API as "Backend Spring Boot"
control ServiceRDV as "Service RendezVous"
database DB as "Base de donnees"

Patient -> Frontend: Choisir medecin + date + heure
Frontend -> API: POST /rendez-vous (donneesRDV)
API -> ServiceRDV: verifierDisponibilite(medecin, creneau)
ServiceRDV -> DB: Rechercher conflits de planning
DB --> ServiceRDV: Statut disponibilite

alt Creneau disponible
  ServiceRDV -> DB: Inserer rendez-vous
  DB --> ServiceRDV: idRendezVous
  ServiceRDV --> API: Confirmation + details
  API --> Frontend: 201 Created
  Frontend --> Patient: Afficher confirmation
else Creneau indisponible
  ServiceRDV --> API: Erreur indisponibilite
  API --> Frontend: 409 Conflict
  Frontend --> Patient: Proposer autres creneaux
end

@enduml
